            <p class="about-content">The photo-sharing website is designed and developed by <%=name %>. <br> <br>
                <strong> Working functionalities:</strong> <br> <br>
                1. Sign up: User can sign up to make a new account. Form Validations included.<br>
                2. Login: User can login with newly created username and password. Server-side validations included.<br>
                3. Logout: User can logout, this ends session and new user can login again. <br>
                4. Profile: When user is logged in, they can view profile and upload file. This file is not saved anywhere on database, yet. <br> 
                5. Discover: User can view uploaded images and image details, but is not allowed to post likes or comments. <br>
                6. Like: A logged-in user can click on 'Like' button on 'Image Details' page to store their like in databse. <br>
                7. Post Comment: A logged-in user can post a comment, this is saved to database. <br>
                8. Show likes: All distinct likes by users are retrived from Database and displayed on this page <br><br>
            
                <strong> Under Development:</strong> <br> <br>
